OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers will continue into the night
OL,7,Falong with the chance of the odd fog
OL,8,Fpatch over Shetland. A band of showery
OL,9,Frain will move over Orkney towards the
OL,10,Fmorning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FCloud and rain over Orkney in
OL,13,Fthe morning will move to Shetland as
OL,14,Fthe rain becomes patchy in the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Sunny spells follow with
OL,16,Fthe odd shower possible for Orkney.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
